data.description: Ideal Washington home near recreation center and schools. Home has a beautiful Pine Mountain view and is nicely upgraded with quartz counters, RV parking, flooring, metal roof, fireplace and a separate 400 square foot underground shop storage and  large parking area. Stunning fireplace and mantel makes this large 5 bedroom home a fantastic property in a great location.
data.whatILove: This home has been fantastic to raise my family of 5. We had plenty of space for each of our children to have their own space as they grew. The yard has been redone through the years. It provides a place for children to play and adults to relax. With space to grow this  home is great for a growing family.
